        "history_title": "History",
        "history_left_copy": "In 1996, Roberto Coin introduced Appassionata, the first collection to feature a hidden ruby, a symbolic signature of fortune, beauty and prosperity. This marked the beginning of the Maison, defined by a unique stylistic approach and guided by the vision and creative energy of its founder.",
        "history_right_copy": "Inspired by art, cultures and imagination, Roberto Coin’s creations are brought to life by master Italian artisans, preserving centuries-old craftsmanship. The brand’s refined yet distinctive style quickly gained international recognition, attracting the worlds of fashion and cinema and establishing its place on the global jewelry scene.",
        "history_ring_drawing": "shopify://shop_images/RC_History-Ring_Drawing.jpg",
        "history_ring_photo": "shopify://shop_images/RC_History-Ring-Cento.jpg",
        "creator_title": "The Creator",
        "creator_copy_1": "Roberto Coin’s journey did not begin in jewelry. After a successful career in luxury hospitality across Europe, he returned to Italy and immersed himself in the goldsmith tradition of Vicenza.",
        "creator_copy_2": "In 1984, he began designing under his own name, transforming experience into creativity and vision into craftsmanship.",
        "creator_image": "shopify://shop_images/Roberto_Coin_the-creator-portrait.jpg",
        "creator_drawing": "shopify://shop_images/RC_History_Vicenza_drawing_image.jpg",
        "ruby_title": "The Ruby",
        "ruby_copy": "<p>Roberto Coin discovered the idea of the signature ruby in ancient legends, where the gem symbolized protection, vitality and passion. Inspired by stories from Egypt, Burma and Hindu mythology, he chose the ruby as the hidden signature of his creations, carrying a message of good fortune, courage and vitality.</p>",
